OL,6,FNineteen children were killed by
OL,7,Fparents who were known domestic
OL,8,Fabusers in the last decade because of
OL,9,Ffailings in the family courts, a
OL,10,Fcharity has said.
OL,12,FWomen's Aid is calling for an urgent
OL,13,Freview of the family justice system
OL,14,Ffollowing a rise in the number of
OL,15,Fchildren being killed by parents who
OL,16,Fhad access rights despite a violent
OL,17,Fhistory.
