OL,3,C19 children killed by a parent due to
OL,4,Caccess 'failings'
OL,6,FThe charity said 67 children had died
OL,7,Fat the hands of perpetrators of
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse in such circumstances
OL,9,Fover the last 30 years.
OL,11,FNineteen of those were between 2015
OL,12,Fand 2024 - a 50% increase on the
OL,13,Fprevious decade. All were aged between
OL,14,Fthree weeks and 11 years old. In all
OL,15,Fbut one case the killer was a man.
OL,16,FFifteen were the child's own father.
OL,18,FThe cases are highlighted in a new
OL,19,Freport by Women's Aid called Nineteen
OL,20,FMore Child Homicides.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
