OL,6,F"This new report exposes the life-
OL,7,Fthreatening consequences of not acting
OL,8,Fon well-document risks of failing to
OL,9,Faddress the pro-contact culture and
OL,10,Fmust be used to finally drive long
OL,11,Foverdue change of the family courts
OL,12,Fresponse to child survivors.
OL,14,F"We must prioritise the safety of
OL,15,Fchildren over an archaic presumption
OL,16,Fand put an end to any more avoidable
OL,17,Fchild deaths."
OL,19,F'Heartbreakingly preventable'
