OL,6,FWomen's Aid said a "pro-contact
OL,7,Fculture" meant dangerous individuals
OL,8,Fwere being given access to children
OL,9,Fdespite the risk.
OL,11,FThe report said there was a "lack of
OL,12,Fprofessional understanding" about
OL,13,Fcoercive control, "a constant
OL,14,Fminimisation of risk" and "significant
OL,15,Fover optimism" that abusive men could
OL,16,Fstill be good fathers.
