OL,6,FThere were "systemic problems" in the
OL,7,Ffamily courts, including unsafe
OL,8,Fcontact between children and
OL,9,Fperpetrators of domestic abuse, the
OL,10,Fcharity said.
OL,12,FCampaigners want the government to
OL,13,Fdrop the "presumption" of parental
OL,14,Finvolvement with children.
OL,16,FClaire Throssell's sons Jack and Paul
OL,17,Fwere killed in a fire started by her
OL,18,Fex-husband Darren Sykes in 2014. Sykes
OL,19,Falso died.
